original_title: GCW: No Signal In The Hills
overview: On August 7th GCW returns to Los Angeles. The event features pro wrestling stars such as Nick Gage, Chris Dickinson, Effy, Tony Deppen, Lee Moriarty, Tree, Ninja Mack, AJ, Allie, Atticus, Dark Sheik, Reefer and more to be announced soon!
